title: Jobs, Green New Deal, Warren Plan to Break Up Big Tech
itunes:title: Jobs, Green New Deal, Warren Plan to Break Up Big Tech
description:
Kevin discusses Friday's disappointing jobs report, the Green New Deal and Senator Elizabeth Warren's plan to break up Big Tech with guests Mattie Dupler, Senior Fellow at the National Taxpayers Union, Alexandra Rojas, Executive Director for the Justice Democrats and Casey Mulligan, Chief Economist for the WH Council of Economic Advisers.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
